en_223464_0	The remains of the Easter Sunday suicide bomber of Zion church in Batticaloa were exhumed from the Kalliyankadu Hindu cemetery today.
en_223464_1	Earlier, Batticaloa Magistrate AC Rizwan ordered the Batticaloa district Secretary to identify a suitable location and bury the remains of the bomber.
en_223464_2	The Court issued a new order to exhume the remains of the bomber from the Kalliyankadu cemetery following protest launched against burying them in a Hindu cemetery.
en_223464_3	Our correspondent stated that the exhumed remains of the bomber is currently lying at Batticaloa hospital.
